high_descs: Turn to your left, take a step, again turn left and move toward the fridge, turn around from the fridge to face a gray table
Pick up the butter knife from the table
Turn around and move to face the fridge
Open the fridge and cut the apple in the fridge, and close the fridge
Turn around and go to the stove
Put the knife on the pan on the stove
Pick up the pan with the knife from the stove
Go back to the gray table
Put the pan on the table
Turn around and go back to the fridge
Open the fridge, pick up a piece of apple, and close the fridge
Take the apple piece to the gray table
Put the apple piece on the pan with the knife
anns.task_desc: Cut a chilled apple, place a piece of it and the knife on the pan on the table

high_descs: Turn to the left, go forward, turn to the left and go across the room to the other side of the black dining table where the lettuce is.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the table.
Turn around, go to the right to the fridge.
Open the fridge, cut the apple inside the fridge into pieces.
Turn around, head left to the stove on the left.
Put the knife into the pan on the back left stove burner.
Pick up the pan containing the knife from the stove.
Turn to the left, go to the right side of the dining table where the lettuce is.
Put the pan down on the table to the left of the lettuce.
Turn around, go to the right to the fridge that is on the left.
Take a piece of the apple out of the fridge.
Go to the left to the dining table where the pan is.
Put the piece of apple into the pan with the knife in it that is on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with apple and a knife in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the side of the black table closer to the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife that is next to the lettuce.
Turn around and walk to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, cut the yellow apple into three pieces then close it.
Turn around then go left to the stove.
Put the knife so it is standing up on the pan on the stove's top left burner.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Turn left and walk back to the black table.
Put the pan with the knife on the table so it is below the potato.
Turn around and walk to face the refrigerator again.
Open the refrigerator, pick up the yellow apple piece to the left then close it.
Turn around and go back to the black table.
Put the apple slice on the pan to the left of the knife on it.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife, yellow apple slice and pan together on the black table.
